2 ohms. So let me erase that

00:03:04.110 --> 00:03:05.620
and simplify our drawing.

00:03:09.020 --> 00:03:10.510
Simplify it.

00:03:10.510 --> 00:03:29.310
So that whole thing could now
be simplified as 2 ohms. I

00:03:29.310 --> 00:03:30.240
